cs></math> is a state space and <math alttext=3D"\mathcal{T}" class=3D"ltx_=
Math" display=3D"inline" id=3D"S2.I2.i1.p1.2.m2" intent=3D":literal"><seman=
tics><mi class=3D"ltx_font_mathcaligraphic">=F0=9D=92=AF</mi><annotation en=
coding=3D"application/x-tex">\mathcal{T}</annotation></semantics></math> is=
 a set of
times (no longer called target times) forming a monoid, whose identity
