c Systems =E2=80=A3 The Stochastic-Quantum Theorem"><span class=3D"ltx_text=
 ltx_ref_tag">1</span></a>) with probabilistic,
or stochastic, behavior. An indivisible stochastic process will
be defined to mean a tuple of the form</p><button class=3D"sr-only button" =
style=3D"display: none;">Report issue for preceding element</button>
