x_ref_tag">4.3</span></a>. For that system, the unitary
time-evolution operator <math alttext=3D"U\mathopen{}\mathclose{{\left(t\le=
ftarrow 0}}\right)\equiv\Sigma^{t/\delta t}" class=3D"ltx_math_unparsed" di=
